<div id="pf5237" class="pf w46 h359" data-page-no="5237"><div class="pc pc5237 w46 h359"><div class="t m5d5 x74 h28 y2f1f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation, incarnation and re-creation, the Godhead is at work, and always </div><div class="t m246 x74 h28 y2d64 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit brings God&apos;s objective to its goal. </div><div class="t m150c x60 h22 y29c0 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What other special role is filled by the Holy Spirit? 2 Peter 1:20, 21. </div><div class="t m55f x4e h28 y299a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Not only did the Holy Spirit inspire the prophets in producing the Scrip-</div><div class="t m1179 x74 h28 y28cd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures but He also has helped people through the ages understand what was </div><div class="t m1142 x74 h28 y2195 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">written. Through His ministry the Scriptures come alive, making Christ real </div><div class="t m1179 x74 h28 y209a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to us today, softening our hearts to the Saviour, and enabling us to live for </div><div class="t m770 x74 h28 y17ec ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him. </div><div class="t m755 x74 h22 y1f68 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SEARCH AND LEARN: What other indications are given of the </div><div class="t m432 x74 h22 y1aeb ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit&apos;s ministry in Old Testament times? </div><div class="t m145d x4e h28 y19ae ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t meb0 x53 h28 y19ae ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen 61 </div><div class="t m5 x30 h28 y1da2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m726 x175 h28 y1da2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m136 x4e h28 y18dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m915 x55 h28 y18dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ex. 31</div><div class="t m755 x19 h28 y18dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m1755 x38 h28 y18dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 </div><div class="t m5 x30 h28 y18dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m726 x175 h28 y18dc ff4 fs